                    <h2><a href="http://www.best-laptop-battery.co.uk/blog/2009/09/18/world-primary-lithium-battery-markets/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to World Primary Lithium Battery Markets">World Primary Lithium Battery Markets</a></h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="postdata">
                        <span class="vcard">Posted by <span class="fn">besbat001</span></span>
                        <span class="published posted_date" title="2009-09-18 20:05:05+00:00">on September 18, 2009</span>
                        <br/>
                        <a href="http://www.best-laptop-battery.co.uk/blog/category/uncategorized/" title="View all posts in Uncategorized" rel="category tag">Uncategorized</a> /
                        <a href="http://www.best-laptop-battery.co.uk/blog/2009/09/18/world-primary-lithium-battery-markets/#respond" title="Comment on World Primary Lithium Battery Markets">No Comments</a>                    </div>
                    <div class="entry-content"><div id="result_box" dir="ltr">This Frost &amp; Sullivan research service entitled World Primary Lithium Market provides in-depth analysis of market revenue, unit shipment analysis and detailed analysis of the global primary <a href="http://www.best-laptop-battery.co.uk/">lithium battery</a> market setting identify drivers and restraints for the market. In this research, expert analysts Frost &amp; Sullivan thoroughly examine the primary market for lithium-based lithium / sulfur dioxide, lithium / thionyl chloride and lithium / manganese dioxide battery chemistries. Geographical analysis of market segments in the market in North America, Europe, Asia Pacific and rest of the world. End-user applications have been reviewed extensively for each primary lithium chemistry batteries.</p>
<p>This analysis is available through our Power Supplies &amp; Batteries Growth Partnership Services program. With this program, clients receive industry-leading market research such as this, with technical and econometric data and many interactive features including Analyst Inquiry Time and Client Councils.</p>
<p>The inherent advantages of Primary Education Drive Adoption Lithium batteries in various applications</p>
<p>Lithium batteries have superior energy density and cycle life compared to other chemistries of the main battery and can last nearly 10 years, making them preferable for critical applications. These <a href="http://www.best-laptop-battery.co.uk/hp-pavilion-dv6000.htm">batteries</a> have operating temperature and exhibit efficient operation in rugged atmospheres. Increasing industrial automation and automation of the manufacturing sector also supports the need for primary lithium batteries.</p>
<p>&#8220;The primary lithium battery market worldwide and generated an estimated $ 1.10 billion in 2007,&#8221; explains the analyst of this research. &#8220;This market is expected to witness growth medium with lithium / manganese dioxide market growing at a significant rate . However, the market is very competitive among the different chemistries of primary lithium batteries. In addition, the threat of lithium-ion also has influence in the growth of certain primary lithium batteries used in select consumer applications.</p>
<p>Military / defense applications and medical equipment market Encourage Lithium significantly</p>
<p>With increased military reconnaissance operations across the world, the need for sophisticated equipment and technologically advanced has increased several folds. Technical advancements, in turn, lead needs higher energy, which stimulates the demand for batteries for a long term and efficient operation. Primary lithium batteries meet these specifications and increasing military budgets and capital spending directly influences the primary battery market. Lithium <a href="http://www.best-laptop-battery.co.uk/dell.htm">batteries</a> are widely used for medical devices in various life support. Many implantable devices, automatic external defibrillators, and infusion pumps prefer primary lithium batteries because they are most suited for medical devices.</p>
<p>One area of concern is that these batteries tend to emit toxic gases and hazardous elements if electrolytes are disclosed. &#8220;These batteries cause environmental pollution when disposal is not handled properly,&#8221; explains the analyst. &#8220;Thus, the manufacture, use and disposal of these batteries involve many regulations to follow, which may affect demand if adequate measures are applied. &#8220;</p></div>
